flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Start of production cycle or completion of a key build point.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawler - Retrieve component dimensions from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: STREAMS - Analyze dimensional data using STREAMS.]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Process Builder - Schedule functional testing based on STREAMS analysis.}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Remote Functions - Perform torque audits and verify fastener integrity.]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Remote Functions - Inspect material and finish quality.]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Remote Functions - Allocate resources for sealing and leakage tests.]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS impacts from rework and scrap, improved OTIF, and increased line throughput.]
  N3 -->|Dimensional inspection fails.| B1[Trigger CWB Lifecycle for manual review and corrective action.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Manual intervention to address dimensional issues.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Functional testing identifies reliabi...| B2[Schedule additional tests and notify relevant teams.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Enhanced reliability through targeted testing.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Torque audit detects joint integrity ...| B3[Increase audit frequency and notify maintenance team.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Improved joint integrity and reduced rework.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]